text: Josue Deprez (born 30 October 1981) is a Haitian judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 73 kg, where he was eliminated by Igor Wandtke in the first round. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Haitian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Haiti Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
